---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'About';
const description = 'About your blog.';
const permalink = `${Astro.site.href}about`;
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} permalink={permalink} current="about" section="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <figure class="about-image">
      <img src="/assets/about-illustration.jpg" alt="Illustration of a notebook" width="330">
    </figure>
    <p>Hello! I’m <strong>Léandre Iskin</strong>. I hold an engineering degree from <strong>ISAE-SUPAERO</strong> and a Master of Engineering in Computer Science from the École Polytechnique de         Montréal. My areas of specialization include <strong>applied mathematics</strong>, <strong>computational science</strong>, and <strong>artificial intelligence</strong>.</p>

    <p>At present, I am working toward a <strong>Ph.D. in Quantitative Finance</strong> at <strong>HEC Montréal</strong>.</p>

    <p>This site is my space to share insights and projects in my fields of interest. You’ll find:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>A <strong>blog</strong> section featuring theoretical results: research articles, intriguing findings, solved exercises, and more.</li>
      <li>A <strong>projects</strong> section showcasing personal and academic work related—directly or indirectly—to my areas of expertise.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>You can learn more about my background by viewing my resume:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>📄 <a href="/assets/resume/Resume_EN.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Download my resume (PDF)</a></li>
      <li>💻 <a href="https://github.com/leandreisk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">My GitHub profile</a></li>
      <li>🌐 <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/léandre-iskin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">My LinkedIn profile</a></li>
      <li>✉️ <a href="mailto:iskinleandre@gmail.com">Contact me by email</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-image {
    float: right;
    margin: -3em -7em 2em 2em;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  .about-image img {
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1020px) {
    .about-image {
      float: none;
      margin: 0 auto 2em;
    }
  }
</style>
